preference.name: MDL_default_attribute_group_types
preference.preference_description: Specifies the list of managed attribute group types available to a specific user role. Valid Values: A list of internal type names of attribute groups and managed attribute groups that are defined in the 4G Designer application. For example: Cpd9PipingManagedAttrGrp Cpd9HVacManagedAttrGrp Cpd9CabinManagedAttrGrp Cpd9DeckManagedAttrGrp Mdl9AttributeGroup
